title: EP 87: Yukmouth Speaks On Beef

description:
On this Christmas Eve episode we tap in w/ the homie Yukmouth from the Luniz and he breaks down his past beefs w/ Fifty Cent, The Game and others. He also speaks on his time at RAP-A-LOT and his loyalty to the iconic label and J.Prince
